          <div style={{ fontSize:11, color:C.faint, fontFamily:mono, marginBottom:8 }}>DEDUPED ACROSS ACTIONS / TARGET DRIFT / PROSPECTS / RADAR / UW FLOW. Review prompts only; no auto-trade.</div>
